{"tid":2214531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[白皮書]The Economic Standard 建議使用羥氯喹（HCQ）","createTime":"2020-09-23T10:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T13:32:07.000Z","uid":294518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7d3fad3a2cde2652193c668195e101b824ae929e","tid":2214531,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T10:18:37.000Z","msg":"The Economic Standard 很榮幸提出我們的第一份白皮書。 我們通過精心分析證明：<br />\n1）羥氯喹（HCQ）是一種安全，用途廣泛的藥物，在過去的中已經為數億人治療了多種疾病。<br />\n 2）大量的受控觀察研究meta-analyses和表明，HCQ可以幫助COVID-19的患者。<br />\n 3）在類似的觀察性研究的基礎上，美國FDA已經批准了數百種藥物，特別是在大量進行meta-analyses時。<br />\n 4）就醫學實踐而言，尤其是在大流行緊急情況下，並非只有隨機對照試驗才能證明採用治療的合理性。<br />\n 5）現在應更廣泛地推薦，處方和推廣HCQ以治療COVID-19。<br />\n 我們的目標是推動有關公共政策的辯論。 與美國和全球各地的執業醫師和傳染病專家密切合作，撰寫本文時沒有任何財政支持或任何形式的道德衝突。 我們非常感謝他們為確保分析準確性提供的幫助。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hcqwhitepaper.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhcqwhitepaper.com%2F&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9rXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=4f62294e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hcqwhitepaper.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/PeterNavarro45/status/1308479130053365761?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPeterNavarro45%2Fstatus%2F1308479130053365761%3Fs%3D20&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9rXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=1be74385\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPeterNavarro45%2Fstatus%2F1308479130053365761%3Fs%3D20&h=54f261f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/PeterNavarro45/status/1308479130053365761?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"8104195853df60564786e4ccc7c0640d8699f474","tid":2214531,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T10:24:06.000Z","msg":"whiter paper PDF<br />\n<a href=\"https://secureservercdn.net/72.167.242.48/u22.f6f.myftpupload.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/HCQWhitePaper.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsecureservercdn.net%2F72.167.242.48%2Fu22.f6f.myftpupload.c